<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_97_r2l17"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / Wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> C . <expan>Pilſach<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd Hanſen Stecʒman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l18">beuolhen etwas <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒü 
<del rend="strikethrough"> Hanſen </del> handeln nu auf den Montag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l19">cʒü <expan>Rietemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Schrannen / als ſie ew das vvol ercʒelen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l20"><expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vvıllen / auf den Montag bey <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l21">doſelbſt cʒü <expan>Ryetemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> ſein wöllet / vnd Jn fürderlıch vnd geraten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l22">ſein / Als wir ew des ſunderlich vvol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd das auch <expan>allcʒ<ex>eit</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_97_r2l23"><expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıene<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>vts<ex>upra</ex></expan> . </ab>
