<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, wir <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan>
<expan>Pilsach<ex>er</ex></expan> und Hansen Steczman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern, bevolhen, etwas
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czü handeln nu <app><note><q type="date">auf den montag</q>31.03.1410</note></app> czü
                                <expan>Rietemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> auf <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        schrannen, als sie ew das wol erczelen <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>.
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen auf den montag bey
                                <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern doselbst czü
                                <expan>Ryetemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> sein wöllet und in fürderlich und
                        geraten sein, als wir ew des sunderlich wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und das auch <expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ew
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>diene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Werpolt <expan>Rawsch<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
